rget framework is compatible. The key change is replacing the old assembly reference with the single `MSTest` v3 meta-package, which bundles the framework, adapter, and test SDK together—so they can remove the old reference and add just the `MSTest` package instead.\n\nSince MSTest v3 maintains backward compatibility with their existing test attributes and assertions, the test code itself shouldn't need any changes.","outputTokens":825,"requestId":"083E:2D9C3A:5529FF:63F0F3:69EAD389"},"id":"17baf3d6-8aa1-482c-8b38-9672bfab8e25","timestamp":"2026-04-24T02:21:11.836Z","parentId":"76dd8201-6bb5-4c92-a28c-8b819a230804"}
